            "replies_count": 1,
            "reblogs_count": 0,
            "favourites_count": 0,
            "edited_at": null,
            "content": "<p><span class=\"h-card\" translate=\"no\"><a href=\"https://graphics.social/@metin\" class=\"u-url mention\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">@<span>metin</span></a></span> </p><p>I\u2019d expect individuals keenly cognizant of reality to act. I want to encourage as many people to take local action:</p><p>pay your town counsel a visit and ask of them:</p><p>Can your community survive indefinitely on the resources available in its territory and in mutual aid pacts with physically adjacent communities?  If not, for how long?</p><p>Climate change is tearing at modernity, fragmenting its productive capacity. It will break. There won\u2019t be a there, there supplying you.</p>",
            "reblog": null,
